title: Kenilworth

description: LibriVox recording of Kenilworth, by Sir Walter Scott. Read by skoval. An Elizabethan era historical novel by Scotland's master of fiction, Sir Walter Scott. With a cast of historical and created characters, including the Queen herself, Scott presents the sad history and tragic consequences of the secretive marriage of young Amy Robsart and the Earl of Leicester.
